{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"story_whispr_set_1_story_1","storyGroup":"story_whispr_set_1","storySort":0,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":null,"storyName":"雨落之前","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"准备离开罗德岛的絮雨接收了一位即将因矿石病失去视力的患者，她想实现对方再看一场电影的愿望。","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"obt/memory/story_whispr_1_1","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":null,"characters":["絮雨","洛拉","蜜莓","温蒂","罗宾"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"Dialog","id":3},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_infirmary","screenadapt":"showall","id":4},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"$drift_loop","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"palysound","name":"$d_gen_doorknockquite","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":10},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","id":11},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":12},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"200","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":13},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":14},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-200","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":15},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","fadetime":"1.5","id":16},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"你好，洛拉。","id":18,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"“......高塔隐没在，水雾之中，淅淅沥沥的雨......落在几千柄伞面上......”","id":20,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"dialog","id":21},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"啊，医生好。","id":23,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"抱歉，打扰了你读书。感觉怎么样？","id":25,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"嗯......受伤的地方没有那么疼了，但还是经常觉得头晕，看不清东西。","id":27,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"现在静脉注射的速度，可以适应吗？有没有觉得不舒服？","id":29,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"手臂有点凉凉的，但是已经习惯啦。","id":31,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"医生，我还要打几天针呀？","id":32,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯......这一点要视情况而定。","id":34,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"会很久吗？我好想出去走走。","id":36,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"我感觉自己好像躺在这里好多天了。明明一动不动，可还是觉得好累。","id":37,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"不会太久的。只是你的伤口还在愈合中，等它长好，你就可以自由活动了。","id":39,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"不过......","id":40,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialog","id":41},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":42},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ri_1","screenadapt":"showall","id":43},{"type":"Character","id":44},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":45},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":46},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","id":47},{"type":"delay","time":"1.2","id":48},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":49},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":50},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"2","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"那个被源石炸弹误伤的孩子，她的血液分析结果也出来了。病情确实还在明显恶化。","id":52,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"虽然恶化速度得到了一定控制，但......唉，毕竟是急性感染，还有多处开放性损伤。我们能为她做的应急处理都做了。","id":53,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"从造影结果来看，她体内的源石已经压迫到了视神经。","id":54,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"1","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯，她自己也感觉到异常了。有时候她会视野模糊。","id":56,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"我们的抑制药物还没能让她的病情稳定下来，以现在的状况来推断......她很可能会失明。","id":57,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"但是，如果现在再告诉她一个新的坏消息的话，那个孩子能不能承受得住呢？","id":58,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"如果躺在床上的人是我的话，或许会觉得，无论是多么残酷的事实，都比一直悬着心却什么也不知道要好。","id":59,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"可是，她还没有意识到害怕，还没有开始做她漫长的噩梦，如果能让她多安心几天的话......","id":60,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialog","id":61},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":62},{"type":"Character","id":63},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":64},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_infirmary","screenadapt":"showall","id":65},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":66},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":67},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":68},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":69},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"我知道，可以自由活动之后，医生们也还要观察一段时间，等我的矿石病病情稳定了，我才可以从罗德岛出院。","id":71,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"不过昨天另一个医生告诉我，罗德岛是一艘很大的船，有医护人员陪同的话，我也可以离开住院部，去逛逛别的地方。","id":72,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"她还从图书室带了本书给我看。","id":73,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"是的，罗德岛很大......你还可以做很多事。","id":75,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"接下来我要给你换药了，不用太在意我这里的工作，请继续看书就好。","id":76,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"那我可以念出声吗？我不想听到药瓶和镊子的声音，有点吓人。","id":78,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯，当然可以。","id":80,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"“忘记带伞的我，看见街道对面的，咖啡厅屋檐下，站着......一个怪人。”","id":82,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"“她......打扮得很......不入时，抱着一把琴，低声地......对着雨幕唱歌。”","id":83,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"“音符，断断续续地朝我飘来，许久我才辨认出，她唱的是......”","id":84,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"......唱的是......呃......","id":85,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"“‘请像忘记初春的雪一样忘记我。’”","id":87,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"......抱歉，我下意识就接话了。","id":88,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":89},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"啊，谢谢你。","id":90,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":91},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"闭眼休息一下吧。或许你是今天看书太久了，眼睛累了，所以有些看不清字。","id":92,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":93},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"医生，你也看过这本书吗？","id":94,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯，不过它改编的电影更有名，我反复看了许多次......听到熟悉的台词，不自觉就说出口了。","id":96,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":97},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"那电影里的主人公长什么样？我觉得她应该是一个红头发、瘦高瘦高的女孩，说话的时候会这样做鬼脸——","id":98,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"——呜！","id":99,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":100},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"请、请不要乱动......脸上的伤口虽然不深，但也需要时间愈合。","id":101,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"嘿嘿。","id":103,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"......电影选择的演员，和你对主人公的想象似乎不太一样。","id":105,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"不过，电影和书讲的本来也不是完全相同的故事。","id":106,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"如果是我的话，可能会更喜欢带着自己的想象把书看完，然后再去看电影如何演绎吧。","id":107,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"好呀，那我也不要你剧透了。等看完这本书，我要自己去看电影。","id":109,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"啊，不过我现在是感染者了......感染者就不能进电影院了。","id":110,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"以前都是妈妈带我去的，两个人可以买一份超大份的爆米花。","id":111,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"她还教我看电影的过程中不许说话。我已经学会了，有看不懂的地方要等到电影结束再问。","id":112,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"我明明是个乖孩子呀......","id":113,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"呜......","id":114,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"......请不要太难过。至少，在罗德岛舰上的多媒体室，也是可以看电影的。","id":116,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"虽然没有电影院那么大的银幕，但如果是独自欣赏，或者几个人一起看电影的话，或许气氛恰好合适。","id":117,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"就算只是沉浸在电影的声音里......","id":118,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":119},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"那等我可以下床活动的时候，医生你要第一时间带我去哦。","id":120,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":121},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"欸，我吗？但是我......","id":122,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialog","id":123},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ri_1","screenadapt":"showall","id":125},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":126},{"type":"character","id":127},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":128},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","id":129},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":130},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":131},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":132},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"2","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"你打算离开罗德岛了？","id":134,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"1","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯，我已经在罗德岛停留很长时间了，不知不觉地，和这里的人也熟悉了起来。","id":136,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"......熟悉到让我开始害怕了。","id":137,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialog","id":138},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":139},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"不、不是说害怕你的意思。","id":140,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"2","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"嗯，我明白的。","id":142,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"你计划好什么时候走了吗？","id":143,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"1","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"最近接收了新的患者，我想等最紧急的状况过去，那之后就离开。","id":145,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"2","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"那，需要我帮你保密吗？","id":147,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"1","id":148},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯，拜托了。我不想说出这些......让人伤心的事情。","id":149,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialog","id":150},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":151},{"type":"Character","id":152},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":153},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_infirmary","screenadapt":"showall","isblock":"true","id":154},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":155},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":156},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":157},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":158},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":159},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"......抱歉，也许我到时候会很忙，所以现在我没办法向你做出承诺。","id":161,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"没关系，那我到时候就去拜托其他医生啦。","id":163,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"药已经换好了。还有什么异样感吗？","id":165,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","focus":"-1","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"没有啦，谢谢你。","id":167,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"啊，稍等，可以麻烦医生调节一下放书的支架吗？书上的字我有些看不清。","id":168,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"矿石病好像把我变成近视了。","id":169,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"不，这其实并不是近视......","id":171,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯，但你的视力确实会受影响，具体受影响程度......我们现在也不能确定。","id":172,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"请多看看书，也多看看窗外漂亮的风景吧。","id":173,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialog","id":174},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":175},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":176},{"type":"Character","id":177},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":178},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_corridor","screenadapt":"showall","id":179},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":180},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.51","id":181},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","fadetime":"0.5","id":182},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":183},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"2","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"所以，那个孩子面临着失明却不自知，希望再看一场电影？","id":185,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"1","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯，我没有办法回答她......无论是真相还是谎言，都太残忍了。","id":187,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"2","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"但是，你是想实现她的愿望的，对吧？","id":189,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"1","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"如果可能的话，我当然很乐意陪她。","id":191,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"而且，要是能收藏一张电影票根的话，那就更好了。毕竟，这会是我在罗德岛看的最后一场电影吧。","id":192,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"只是，她很可能看不到了......","id":193,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"2","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"之前罗德岛办的那些相对正式的电影放映会，从场地布置和技术需求来说，倒是非常简单。","id":195,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"1","id":196},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"你是觉得......我应该答应那个孩子吗？","id":197,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"2","id":198},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"这件事当然是由作为医生的你来决定。","id":199,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"我只是认为，即使不是为了别人，只是作为你自己离开罗德岛前的纪念，你也可以举办一次放映会，然后留下电影票根。","id":200,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"1","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"只是为了我自己的事情......","id":202,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"但是，恐怕我也不知道该找谁帮忙布置一个临时影院。","id":203,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"2","id":204},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"别担心，这些我应该能帮你做到。虽然跟我的部门不相关，但这只是个简单的小工程。","id":205,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"如果你只是需要凭电影票入场......对，也许再加上能自助买票检票，不需要工作人员值守的话，对你来说更舒适一些。","id":206,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"1","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"谢谢......","id":208,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_400_weedy_1","focus":"2","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"没事，这对我来说算不了什么。","id":210,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"温蒂","text":"希望你能留下一段美好的回忆。","id":211,"figure":"char_400_weedy_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":212},{"type":"Dialog","id":213},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":214},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":215},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":216},{"type":"Character","id":217},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_infirmary","screenadapt":"coverall","id":218},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":219},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"$path_loop","volume":"0.4","id":220,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":221},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":222},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","fadetime":"0.5","id":223},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":224},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"医生好。","id":226,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"你是......那个会给我讲电影的医生吗？","id":227,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":228},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"抱歉，我不太看得清，只能通过脚步声辨认......如果我认错了的话，对不起。","id":229,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":230},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"......没有，你没认错。你好，洛拉。","id":231,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":232},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"啊，那就好。","id":233,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"医生，我该叫你什么名字呀？许多医生都戴着工牌，但是你没有。","id":234,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":235},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"啊，请不要在意我的名字......","id":236,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"我要做新一轮的身体检查了。","id":237,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"嗯，好。","id":239,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"医生，我其实有点害怕......","id":241,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"我的视力越来越差，可是大家都不告诉我这是怎么了。","id":242,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"我知道矿石病是治不好的，但是，我还没做好准备......我是不是要......","id":243,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"请不要太过担心。暂时来说，你是不会有生命危险的。","id":245,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"在你身上，矿石病的病情已经逐渐稳定下来了，腹部和腿部的创伤也愈合得很好。","id":246,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"这次检查结果出来之后，医生们就可以确定什么时候给伤口拆线。","id":247,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"很快......也许再过两天，你就可以去看电影了。","id":248,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":249},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"真的吗？","id":250,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":251},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯......对了。","id":252,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"正好，最近罗德岛会放映一场电影，就是你在看的这本书所改编的。","id":253,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"等你可以自由活动的时候，我们一起去看吧。","id":254,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":255},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"哇！说好了哦！","id":256,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":257},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯，说好了。","id":258,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":259},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"那......检查的时候可以继续给我讲这个故事吗？","id":260,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"我也想自己看书，但是我现在看书有点吃力......","id":261,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"我明白的。","id":263,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"请闭上眼睛，稍微休息一下吧。","id":264,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialog","id":265},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":266},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.7","id":267},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.6","id":268},{"type":"move","name":"right","ypos":"-50","fadetime":"1.8","block":"false","id":269},{"type":"character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"0.5","id":270},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":271},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"100","fadetime":"1.5","id":272},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":273},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_empty","focus":"1","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"我记得，昨天我们在说主角和来自过去的吟游诗人，抵达了莱塔尼亚的一座移动城市。","id":275,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_empty","focus":"2","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"嗯。","id":277,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_empty","focus":"1","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"吟游诗人从来没有进入过移动城市，只是乘坐入口的升降梯，她就被吓坏了。","id":279,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_empty","focus":"2","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"对于吟游诗人来说，城市应该很吵吧。","id":281,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_empty","focus":"1","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯，非常吵。她靠自己灵敏的耳朵分辨音律，而这双灵敏的耳朵，在城市里捕捉到的都是噪音。","id":283,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"她也从没有见过那些机械校准的、镶嵌着施术单元的乐器，它们演奏出的乐声本身就像是一种源石技艺，让她流连忘返。","id":284,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"而且，这座城市对她很亲热，许多高塔的主人邀请她成为自己的宾客。","id":285,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_empty","focus":"2","id":286},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"可是她是来自过去的人呀，她还要想办法回去呢。","id":287,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_empty","focus":"1","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯......她其实没有可以回去的地方。","id":289,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_empty","focus":"2","id":290},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"为什么？","id":291,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"——啊，要不就留个悬念吧！等看电影的时候，让我亲眼看到结局是什么。","id":292,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_empty","focus":"1","id":293},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"......对了，洛拉。","id":294,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_empty","focus":"2","id":295},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"嗯？","id":296,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"char_empty","focus":"1","id":297},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"......看电影的时候，除了看画面，其实还可以听到很多声音。","id":298,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"吟游诗人拨动琴弦低声吟唱，羽兽在高空鸣叫，长风穿过他们漫游的林海，雨簌簌落在林间小屋的檐瓦上......","id":299,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"如果是借用多媒体室放映电影，也可以小声讲话。","id":300,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"到时候，要是你有......看不清的地方，我还是会讲给你听的。","id":301,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialog","id":302},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":303},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ri_1","screenadapt":"showall","id":304},{"type":"Character","id":305},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":306},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":307},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":308},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":309},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":310},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"2","id":311},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"絮雨小姐，要休息一下，来一块莓果干吗？","id":312,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"1","id":313},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"谢谢......但、但是不必了，看完洛拉的检查结果之后，我还要去照顾别的病人。","id":314,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"2","id":315},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"要注意适时放松哦，你自己的身体也不太好，不要只照顾别人呀。","id":316,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"1","id":317},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"谢谢，请不必太担心。","id":318,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"2","id":319},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"对了，你之前说带洛拉去看电影，是说周六的那场放映会吗？","id":320,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"1","id":321},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"是。","id":322,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"2","id":323},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"唉，那你有告诉她最坏的预测吗？有可能她到时已经什么都看不到了，只能靠听觉。","id":324,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"1","id":325},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"我......还没有。这些天以来，去看一场电影就是她最大的期盼，我不想让她太早失望。","id":326,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"2","id":327},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"嗯，无论如何，要是能让她重新体验事故发生之前的日常小事，她的精神压力也会有些许缓解吧。","id":328,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"等她身体状况稳定下来之后，我就带着零食去找她聊聊天。","id":329,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"当然啦，我也会给你带的，下次一定要吃哦！","id":330,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"1","id":331},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"下次吗？......嗯，谢谢你。","id":332,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"2","id":333},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"对了，只要是最近来谈话室的干员们，我都推荐去参加周末的放映会好啦。","id":334,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"人多一点的话，感觉会更像电影院吧？也能让患者重新建立与人群接触的信心。","id":335,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"1","id":336},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯......谢谢。我会记住罗德岛的这一切......","id":337,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialog","id":338},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":339},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-80","fadetime":"1","id":340},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"——稍等，蜜莓医生。请来看这个。","id":341,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":342},{"type":"Dialog","id":343},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":344},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":345},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":346},{"type":"Character","id":347},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":348},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"showall","id":349},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":350},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.9","id":351},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":352},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"$warm_loop","volume":"0.5","id":353,"musicid":2},{"type":"Text","text":"走吧走吧，放映会要开始啦！","id":354},{"type":"Text","text":"是谁组织的？","id":355},{"type":"Text","text":"嗯......不知道，也看不出来。我是被蜜莓推荐来的。","id":356},{"type":"Text","text":"这里既没有宣传单也没有告示，好像就是一夜之间在多媒体室搭起来了一个迷你电影院。","id":357},{"type":"Text","text":"也没有人在门口检票，都是自助打印电影票。","id":358},{"type":"Text","text":"不过，既然我们能打印出电影票，那意思应该就是我们可以进吧？没有说不让看吧？","id":359},{"type":"Text","text":"哎，这部电影我好奇很久了，自从之前看到絮雨的影评，我就一直想找机会欣赏一下。","id":360},{"type":"Text","text":"嗯，我也是！","id":361},{"type":"Dialog","id":362},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":363},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.4","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":364},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","fadetime":"1","id":365},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":366},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":367},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"洛拉，请小心。","id":368,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":369},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"没事的，医生，虽然有点黑，但这么高的台阶我怎么会看不清呢！","id":370,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"咦，这里真的好像电影院呀，还有不少人......我可以进去吗？","id":371,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":372},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"请不要担心，你和其他人的日常接触，是不会让他们感染矿石病的。","id":373,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":374},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"那我就坐在第一排啦。","id":375,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"这么大的屏幕......我自己就可以看清欸。","id":376,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"医生，你有事要忙的话，就不用陪我啦，等会儿我能自己找到回病房的路。","id":377,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":378},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"不，请让我留在这里，再看一遍这个故事吧。","id":379,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialog","id":380},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$slideshow","channel":"bag","volume":"2","id":381},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":382},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":383},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bag","fadetime":"1","id":384},{"type":"Character","id":385},{"type":"Dialog","id":386},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ri_1","screenadapt":"showall","id":387},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":388},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","id":389},{"type":"delay","time":"1.6","id":390},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":391},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":392},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":393},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"1","id":394},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"——稍等，蜜莓医生。请来看这个。","id":395,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"从这几张造影检测结果对比来看，源石在洛拉体内的扩散......控制住了。","id":396,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"2","id":397},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"哇......真的！","id":398,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"这样，你们可以好好地一起看电影啦。","id":399,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"1","id":400},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"嗯......","id":401,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_449_glider_1$1","focus":"2","id":402},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"你还有什么担忧的事情吗？","id":403,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"有什么心事的话，或许可以告诉我哦。无论是高兴还是难过的事，把它说出来都会让人感觉更好一些。","id":404,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"不用担心，我可是有资格认证的心理辅导者，你不会给我增加负担的。","id":405,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蜜莓","text":"而且，不说出来的话，你也不知道其他人会作何反应呀。","id":406,"figure":"avg_449_glider_1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":407},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":408},{"type":"Character","id":409},{"type":"Background","id":410},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":411},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0","keep":"true","id":412},{"type":"Dialog","id":413},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":414},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":415},{"type":"Character","id":416},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":417},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_corridor","screenadapt":"showall","id":418},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":419},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":420},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":421},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","fadetime":"0.5","id":422},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":423},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":424},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"这部电影......我总觉得还没有看懂结局，但是心里又有模模糊糊的想法。","id":425,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"啊，医生，你在哭吗？","id":426,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":427},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"请不要在意......只是每一次听到结束的音乐，都会触动许多思绪。","id":428,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"这个结局，人们向来有各自不同的理解。甚至我自己在不同的心境下去看，也会产生不一样的想法。","id":429,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":430},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"那就等我长大一些之后，再来重看这部电影吧。","id":431,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"谢谢你呀，医生，陪了我这么长时间。","id":432,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":433},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"请稍等一下，洛拉......","id":434,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"抱歉，我有很重要的事情，还没有告诉你。","id":435,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":436},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"嗯？","id":437,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":438},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"就如你感觉到的一样，你的视力受到了矿石病的影响，在逐渐下降。","id":439,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"虽然现在病情暂时抑制住了，但源石对人体的侵蚀......终究是不可逆的过程。","id":440,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":441},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"意思是，我会变得什么都看不见吗？","id":442,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":443},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"......是的。我不能判断失明会在什么时间出现，但它离你并不远。","id":444,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":445},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"呼......","id":446,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"其实，我之前就差不多猜到啦。","id":447,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":448},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"对不起，我一直没有告诉你......","id":449,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":450},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"没事的呀，医生，我已经好好想过了，甚至做好了看不到电影的准备。","id":451,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":452},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"所以这些天来，我一直都努力睁大眼睛，记住自己看见的街道和房子，看见的花花草草。记住天是蓝色的，雪是白色的。","id":453,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":454},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"我不知道矿石病什么时候又会让我的身体痛起来......不知道我哪一天睁眼就会变得什么也看不见。","id":455,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"但是在那之前，我还想努力把我遇到的一切刻进自己的脑海里。","id":456,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"......还想记住我喜欢的人，照顾我的人。","id":457,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":458},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"这样以后听到那些名字，我还能想起他们的样子。","id":459,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"就算事情真的像我听说的那样，所有东西都会慢慢被忘记，就像上了年纪的爷爷变得不知道我是谁。","id":460,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":461},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"就算总有一天......","id":462,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":463},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"就算总有一天我听到一部电影的名字，再也想不起来它对我来说意味着什么。","id":464,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"就像电影的结局里，走进雨幕消失的吟游诗人......她也曾经在这个时代的雨中起舞过。","id":465,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"啊，抱歉，我又自顾自接话了。","id":466,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"2","id":467},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"可是你说的就是我心里的感觉呀。","id":468,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"洛拉","text":"对啦，你觉得那个结局，吟游诗人最后是回去了吗？还是留在了我们身边呢？","id":469,"figure":"avg_npc_045"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","name2":"avg_npc_045","focus":"1","id":470},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"现在的话，我觉得......","id":471,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialog","id":472},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.51","id":473},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":474},{"type":"Character","name":"char_empty","id":475},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":476},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"-200","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":477},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":478},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"200","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":479},{"type":"Character","name":"char_451_robin","fadetime":"1","id":480},{"type":"delay","time":"2.2","id":481},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":482},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"啊，是经常出现在多媒体室的那位......","id":483,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_451_robin","id":484},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗宾","text":"（点头）","id":485,"figure":"char_451_robin"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":486},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"（点头）","id":487,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_451_robin","id":488},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗宾","text":"......下周六，我打算借多媒体室放映《记忆漂流》。","id":489,"figure":"char_451_robin"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗宾","text":"你来看吗？","id":490,"figure":"char_451_robin"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_436_whispr","id":491},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"下周六吗？","id":492,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"絮雨","text":"......嗯，我会来的。谢谢你的邀请。","id":493,"figure":"char_436_whispr"},{"type":"Dialog","id":494},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":495},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":496},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":497},{"type":"Character","id":498},{"type":"Image","id":499}],"characters":["絮雨","洛拉","蜜莓","温蒂","罗宾"]}